zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533119\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533119\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vpp1665702671467.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vpp1665702671467.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vpp1665702671467.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vpp1665702671467\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the color and border properties for all panels and toolbars in the application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__section_w2865ab1b5b1_w2866ab1b5_w2867ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17555e1_d17556e1_d17557e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__section_rrl_tqc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230793e90\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">panel</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">upanel(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertiesList</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__section_ayw_yqc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230793e112\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertiesList</var>—semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Panel properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> Property </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\"> More Information </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BackColor</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Background color of the panel and panel\n                        buttons. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BackColorFill</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Style of the background color:\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">flat</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">gradient</code>. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpd1665702587794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpd1665702587794.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background color is styled with a flat or gradient color.\">Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BackColorHover</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Color of the panel button when the mouse\n                        hovers over it. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixw1665702632664.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixw1665702632664.html\" title=\"Color of a tab or panel button when the mouse hovers over it.\">Hover Background Color ( BackColorHover)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BackColorLocked</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Color of the button when the it is selected\n                        and stays depressed. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcf1665703117419.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcf1665703117419.html\" title=\"Color of the panel button when it is selected and stays selected. Valid value is a web color name, system color name, or an RGB hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). (Decimal RGB colors are not supported.)\">BackColorLocked</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BackColorSelect</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Background color of the selected panel item. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ovj1665702629207.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ovj1665702629207.html\" title=\"Background color of a tab, menu item, or panel button when it has been selected.\">Active Background Color (BackColorSelect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BorderColorHover</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Color of the border when the mouse cursor\n                        rests on a panel button. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vry1665703117492.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vry1665703117492.html\" title=\"Color of the border when the mouse cursor rests on a panel button.\">BorderColorHover</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BorderColorLocked</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Color of the panel button border when it is\n                        selected and stays selected. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uab1665703117640.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uab1665703117640.html\" title=\"Color of the panel button border when the button stays depressed. A web color name, system color name, or an RGB hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). (Decimal RGB colors are not supported.)\">BorderColorLocked</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1\"> BorderColorSelect</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2\"> Color of the border around a selected panel\n                        button. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vyb1665702851141.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyb1665702851141.html\" title=\"Color of the border around a selected menu item or panel button. Valid value is a web or system color name, or a hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark). If not specified, the Windows system default is used.\">BorderColorSelect</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" headers=\"vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__1 vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__2 vpp1665702671467__table_d17558e1_d17559e1_d17560e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__note_xdh_krc_xvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> When a color property is not defined, the\n                           Windows default is used.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__section_yjh_mrc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230793e325\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Panel</span> setting control the appearance of all panels and\n            toolbars in the application. The specified properties are only applied if the\n               <span class=\"keyword option\">ButtonStyle</span> setting is set to 9 (user-defined). For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__pre_k2h_nrc_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[application]\nPanel = upanel(backcolor=control)\n\n[upi]\nButtonStyle=9</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"vpp1665702671467__note_w2868ab1b5b7b7_w2869ab1b5b7_w2870ab1b5_w2871ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> Using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Panel</span> setting bypasses the Windows\n            theme manager, so you need to explicitly specify all the properties you want to\n            control.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zja1665702873395.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Panels</a><p>Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/avj1665702614940.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ButtonStyle</a><p>Specifies a style for the appearance of buttons and borders in the Uniface toolbar and panels.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533119\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533119\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Panel Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the color and border properties for all panels and toolbars in the application. Default value: None File section: [application] Syntax panel { = } upanel( PropertiesList ) Arguments PropertiesList —semi-colon delimited list of property-value pairs. Table 1. Panel properties Property Description More Information BackColor Background color of the panel and panel buttons. Background Color (BackColor) BackColorFill Style of the background color: flat or gradient . Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill) BackColorHover Color of the panel button when the mouse hovers over it. Hover Background Color ( BackColorHover) BackColorLocked Color of the button when the it is selected and stays depressed. BackColorLocked BackColorSelect Background color of the selected panel item. Active Background Color (BackColorSelect) BorderColorHover Color of the border when the mouse cursor rests on a panel button. BorderColorHover BorderColorLocked Color of the panel button border when it is selected and stays selected. BorderColorLocked BorderColorSelect Color of the border around a selected panel button. BorderColorSelect Note: When a color property is not defined, the Windows default is used. Description Use the Panel setting control the appearance of all panels and toolbars in the application. The specified properties are only applied if the ButtonStyle setting is set to 9 (user-defined). For example: ;usys.ini [application] Panel = upanel(backcolor=control) [upi] ButtonStyle=9 Copy Important: Using the Panel setting bypasses the Windows theme manager, so you need to explicitly specify all the properties you want to control. Related Links Panels Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations. ButtonStyle Specifies a style for the appearance of buttons and borders in the Uniface toolbar and panels. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}